---
import { Container } from "@components/Container";
import { SectionTitle, TypographyAstro } from "@components/Typography";
import { cubeSide, Eye } from "src/assets";
---

<div class="bg-brand-black py-20">
  <Container>
    <SectionTitle
      type="Advantages"
      title="Nothing kills business faster than a entry-level developers"
      colorTitle="text-brand-white"
    />
    <section class="grid grid-cols-2 grid-rows-5 md:grid-cols-4 md:grid-rows-4">
      <video
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        class="md:col-span-2 md:row-span-2 h-full w-full object-cover"
      >
        <source src={cubeSide} type="video/mp4" /></video
      >

      <div class="row-start-1 col-start-2 md:row-start-auto md:col-start-auto">
      </div>

      <article
        class="xl:p-4 p-2 border-r md:border border-brand-white row-start-1 md:row-start-auto"
      >
        <h6
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white xl:font-bold",
            "text-16 md:text-14 lg:text-16 xl:text-18 2xl:text-20",
            "mb-3 2xl:mb-6",
          ]}
        >
          EXPERT TEAM
        </h6>
        <p
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white font-gothic",
            "text-12 md:text-10 lg:text-12 xl:text-base 2xl:text-20",
            "2xl:tracking-1",
          ]}
        >
          Stellar team, you would otherwise not have access to. Our community
          consists of more than 90% of senior developers and project managers
          with a T-shaped skill set.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="xl:p-4 p-2 border-t border-brand-white">
        <h6
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white xl:font-bold",
            "text-16 md:text-14 lg:text-16 xl:text-18 2xl:text-20",
            "mb-3 2xl:mb-6",
          ]}
        >
          Remote Convenience
        </h6>
        <p
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white font-gothic",
            "text-12 md:text-10 lg:text-12 xl:text-base 2xl:text-20",
            "2xl:tracking-1",
          ]}
        >
          100% remote and always just a click away. We ensure seamless
          communication and collaboration, no matter where you are.
        </p>
      </article>

      <div class="hidden md:block"></div>
      <div class="hidden md:block"></div>

      <article
        class="xl:p-4 p-2 border-r border-b md:border-l md:border-t border-brand-white"
      >
        <h6
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white xl:font-bold",
            "text-16 md:text-14 lg:text-16 xl:text-18 2xl:text-20",
            "mb-3 2xl:mb-6",
          ]}
        >
          Empathetic Approach
        </h6>
        <p
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white font-gothic",
            "text-12 md:text-10 lg:text-12 xl:text-base 2xl:text-20",
            "2xl:tracking-1",
          ]}
        >
          We approach every project with empathy and understanding that every
          client has unique pains and needs.
        </p>
      </article>

      <div class="text-white"></div>
      <div class="md:hidden"></div>

      <article class="xl:p-4 p-2 md:border border-brand-white">
        <h6
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white xl:font-bold",
            "text-16 md:text-14 lg:text-16 xl:text-18 2xl:text-20",
            "mb-3 2xl:mb-6",
          ]}
        >
          Efficient Execution
        </h6>
        <p
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white font-gothic",
            "text-12 md:text-10 lg:text-12 xl:text-base 2xl:text-20",
            "2xl:tracking-1",
          ]}
        >
          We excel in project management ensuring that your project is executed
          efficiently and effectively.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="xl:p-4 p-2 md:border-l md:border-b border-brand-white">
        <h6
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white xl:font-bold",
            "text-16 md:text-14 lg:text-16 xl:text-18 2xl:text-20",
            "mb-3 2xl:mb-6",
          ]}
        >
          Values-Driven
        </h6>
        <p
          class:list={[
            "text-brand-white font-gothic",
            "text-12 md:text-10 lg:text-12 xl:text-base 2xl:text-20",
            "2xl:tracking-1",
          ]}
        >
          We are deeply committed to our values of decency, meaningful
          engagement, standards, and synergy, which reflect in everything we do.
        </p>
      </article>

      <div class="hidden md:block"></div>

      <figure class="border border-brand-white">
        <img src={Eye.src} alt="Eye image" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
      </figure>
    </section>
  </Container>
</div>

<style>
  .container-aspect > * {
    aspect-ratio: 1/1;
  }
</style>
